name: Full moon, November 2024
summary: The full moon in November 2024, also known as the Super Beaver Moon, will be the last supermoon of the year. Supermoons are full moons that occur when the Moon is at its closest point to Earth, making it appear larger and brighter. The full moon in November 2024 will be in the sign of Taurus, which is associated with stability, practicality, and sensuality. This full moon is said to be a time for reevaluating one's worth and self-care routines. It is also said to be a good time for setting new goals and intentions for the future.

name: King Charles
summary: King Charles III celebrated his 76th birthday with several notable events. He attended the Remembrance Sunday ceremony at the Cenotaph, where he laid a wreath to honor fallen soldiers. The King also visited a food poverty project on his birthday, highlighting his commitment to addressing social issues. Additionally, King Charles and the Princess of Wales attended a Paris Olympics reception, where the Princess Royal stepped in for Queen Camilla. Prince Andrew secured funds to remain at the Royal Lodge, while the King received birthday greetings from the Royal Family. Despite acknowledging his "advancing years," the King celebrated his birthday with a new picture release and received an emotional reaction from a film about domestic abuse.
